					<description><![CDATA[随着社会的发展，现在的人们一年四季都可以吃到各种各样的水果，也完全不需要担心吃不饱的问题，相反，摄入的热量太多 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1">随着社会的发展，现在的人们一年四季都可以吃到各种各样的水果，也完全不需要担心吃不饱的问题，相反，摄入的热量太多，减肥倒是成了一个令人头大的问题，一边是美味的食物诱惑我们，一边是健康问题刻不容缓，所以很多想要减肥的小姑娘就会选择用水果代替餐食，后知后觉才得知有些水果的糖分并不比米饭少，不仅不利于减肥瘦身，还会适得其反。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-680" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d5cbce04ab67ff4d92af95d144c59f14-1024x894.jpg" width="1024" height="894" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d5cbce04ab67ff4d92af95d144c59f14-1024x894.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d5cbce04ab67ff4d92af95d144c59f14-300x262.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d5cbce04ab67ff4d92af95d144c59f14-768x670.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d5cbce04ab67ff4d92af95d144c59f14.jpg 1054w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2">不提倡通过节食换食的方法减肥，不过可以推荐给大家一些含糖量低的水果。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="4">一、圣女果</h1>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-681" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f505048ff7ee840d21cdf639f665af6c-768x1024.jpg" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f505048ff7ee840d21cdf639f665af6c-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f505048ff7ee840d21cdf639f665af6c-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f505048ff7ee840d21cdf639f665af6c.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="5">乍一听名字很洋气，其实就是我们平时常见的小番茄，它富含高纤维，低糖分，因此很适合追剧观影时候当做闲嘴零食食用，吃很多也不用担心会长胖，经常食用还有美容养颜的效果，但是要提醒大家，圣女果是偏酸性的，如果有胃溃疡或者肠胃不舒服的人要慎重食用，并且最好不要空腹食用，会刺激肠胃。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-682" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4d709b463685ddf9c441f4210b1e96a8-768x1024.jpg" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4d709b463685ddf9c441f4210b1e96a8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4d709b463685ddf9c441f4210b1e96a8-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4d709b463685ddf9c441f4210b1e96a8.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">圣女果挑选小知识：通常而言小的果子要比大的果子甜，但也不能太小，因为太小的圣女果通常是没长熟的或者发育不全的，然后就要摸一下表皮，圣女果的果子越新新鲜果实就越硬，外皮干皱发软的就不要买了，最后看一下颜色，颜色越深说明阳光越充足，果实越甜。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="19">二、菠萝</h1>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-683" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1bd9297052530984dcb8a929dcf322c3.png" width="540" height="960" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1bd9297052530984dcb8a929dcf322c3.png 540w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1bd9297052530984dcb8a929dcf322c3-169x300.png 169w" sizes="(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9">菠萝因为其酸酸甜甜的口感一直深受人们的喜爱，在茶余饭后来一块，还可以帮助消化，菠萝的热量也很低，吃多了也不用担心会长胖，并且菠萝还十分解馋，又香又甜谁能不爱呢？不过建议大家不要空腹食用菠萝，菠萝也是酸性水果，避免引起肠胃的不舒服。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-684" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/bc492733b7ea5f725c6f50b9c286a446.jpg" width="624" height="832" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/bc492733b7ea5f725c6f50b9c286a446.jpg 624w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/bc492733b7ea5f725c6f50b9c286a446-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10">菠萝挑选小知识：通常叶子长一些的更好吃，菠萝的颜色呈现明黄色是比较熟一些的，绿色的生一些的。可以按一下，软一些的熟得透一些，比较甜，但也不能太软，都凹陷进去的那种，那就是变质了，熟的菠萝香气更浓一些，可以试着闻一下。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="20">三、苹果</h1>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-685" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/24b4d1b443676ea4dfea3e327166ff07.jpg" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/24b4d1b443676ea4dfea3e327166ff07.jpg 640w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/24b4d1b443676ea4dfea3e327166ff07-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="13">一提到苹果，大家想到应该就是甜甜的，营养很全面，但其实苹果的热量并不高，常见的苹果品种一百克大约含有六十大卡的热量，而且富含多种维生素，这些营养称为可溶性强，人体容易吸收，可以说苹果在健康方面是全球公认的棒，有句话说得好，一天一苹果，医生远离我。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-686" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/208c865ff31e83b3b1dbc3c06452f247.jpg" width="600" height="800" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/208c865ff31e83b3b1dbc3c06452f247.jpg 600w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/208c865ff31e83b3b1dbc3c06452f247-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="14">苹果挑选小知识：首先要看颜色，并不是越鲜艳越好，黄里透红的苹果一般比较甜，然后就要看果脐，一般来说甜的苹果果脐凹陷比较深，凹陷浅的苹果一般比较酸，其次是摸一下果皮，一般来说越粗糙说明受到的光照越好，就越甜，最后垫一下重量，选重一点的会更好。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-687" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/618bb76b891c311c3bd788aaea3a6c32-768x1024.jpg" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/618bb76b891c311c3bd788aaea3a6c32-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/618bb76b891c311c3bd788aaea3a6c32-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/618bb76b891c311c3bd788aaea3a6c32.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="15">另外提醒大家，我们见到苹果表面有一些白色的粉末，那不是农药残留奥，而是苹果自身分泌的一种果蜡，可以避免水分流失和病虫侵入果肉，对人体无害。</p>
